I felt compelled to write a brief review because this place only has 1 star.
I was in here last night.
Nothing spectacular, nothing awful.
Hence the 3 star rating.
I was looking for something specific so I needed help finding it.
None of the employees asked if I was finding everything okay, but when I found someone to point me in the right direction, she was polite and took me to the section, then explained all of my options.
She made sure it was exactly what I was looking for.
Also, the cashier was outgoing and had a fun personality.
She even made me laugh.
=) I asked if they could give any kind of discount since what I was purchasing is for the cause of raising money to send homeless children to a summer sports camp and the manager approved.
All in all, I had a decent experience here and left with a smile on my face.

